{"tid":560930,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人試過睇戲入錯院。。。","createTime":"2018-02-14T14:14:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-22T17:38:58.000Z","uid":51346,"like":223,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":53,"replies":[{"pid":"13f4f339d14a07f4a587b7a9e7ebd86ada1f3e43","tid":560930,"uid":51346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T14:14:38.000Z","msg":"心諗個預告做咩咁長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"435d8a4aad5cfce06664bc4072b3f15de5de3025","tid":560930,"uid":51346,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T02:30:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0baaba5fdaf263e09d76242c19567325bbf0b23b","tid":560930,"uid":6429,"like":171,"dislike":2,"score":169,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T02:46:49.000Z","msg":"遲到 仲要入錯人地個院 <br />\n人地個院做緊Annabelle 一打開塊黑布全場望住我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n臨走望左下個mon 咁啱係驚嚇位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0c5b11685ba24ebf2287b41a64bee2f05b7bf84","tid":560930,"uid":4402,"like":584,"dislike":12,"score":572,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T02:49:17.000Z","msg":"睇玩轉極樂園<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 無啦啦播冰雪奇緣 以為入錯院"},{"pid":"1889fbe4aca72abf0c6f59ce34e9541974670394","tid":560930,"uid":152123,"like":95,"dislike":0,"score":95,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T03:05:50.000Z","msg":"我堂細佬<br />\n想睇球皇比利 點知入錯屍殺列車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fe0d1ac5bfce73d671fe11000bec6397b8396fc","tid":560930,"uid":1473,"like":1,"dislike":49,"score":-48,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T03:08:12.000Z","msg":"試過買錯日子，到坐個陣比人趕先知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過最後坐前少少睇"},{"pid":"38cc2ec2a234d8aacf9a861caf3bc2e31d6c8acf","tid":560930,"uid":50327,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T03:18:26.000Z","msg":"試過入岩戲院, 不過早左半場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94d46df95dd73ccc3b2ad975b13aa63ffbd42df4","tid":560930,"uid":51346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T04:15:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b148c5c6353aa859dd7bbd5bd16b12a0475a625","tid":560930,"uid":73849,"like":203,"dislike":4,"score":199,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T07:40:57.000Z","msg":"同一日、同一套戲、同一集團嘅戲院，<br />\n正常搣完飛行入去，<br />\n入到院搵唔到我哋要坐嗰行已經心知不妙，<br />\n行返出去望真啲張飛，<br />\n原來個FD買咗A戲院嘅飛但約咗我哋去B戲院<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n兩場開場時間又差唔多，門口個職員又搣咗張飛我哋都不以為意，<br />\n最後拿拿聲上網睇下邊個位未有人買飛，即刻坐低睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3c73467cc750dd6b2f941963adfabd19762d502","tid":560930,"uid":51346,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T09:02:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92fb555b0f892f8dec5b6d991139b6819e676eb3","tid":560930,"uid":64694,"like":67,"dislike":0,"score":67,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T09:05:54.000Z","msg":"頂, 睇錯咗入錯戲院<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a50074ecf34892b8916574f4a4e4cc6d42822f3a","tid":560930,"uid":51346,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"92fb555b0f892f8dec5b6d991139b6819e676eb3","tid":560930,"uid":64694,"like":67,"dislike":0,"score":67,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T09:05:54.000Z","msg":"頂, 睇錯咗入錯戲院<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T14:56:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6