Z","msg":"之前去台灣旅行無聊就去左睇spider man<br />\n咁我同frd買飛個陣已經開左場一陣<br />\n入到場勁黑咁搵我地個位 <br />\n點知發現我地個位俾人坐左<br />\n心諗啲台灣人睇戲係唔跟位坐架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n企左陣諗點算好 就有人叫我地求其坐住先 <br />\n點知成場勁full得返勁入既單丁位 仲要同frd分開坐<br />\n終於sip左入去坐低睇啦 咁一望已經有怪獸出左黎破壞緊<br />\n坐左5分鐘覺得唔對路 點解睇黎睇去都唔似spider man d 怪獸<br />\n咁就問隔離位呢套係咪蜘蛛俠<br />\n佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：你說這套嗎？這是哥吉拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n即刻同個frd 勁柒咁sip返出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82797166cd179c0c23280ecf1f671ef3e5991381","tid":560930,"uid":51346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T10:05:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"669767283c0fd0d421fb3626bffed0fd19cbf327","tid":560930,"uid":2222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T10:16:17.000Z","msg":"前排喺mcl 買咗場睇新神奇四俠，點知佢出錯咗飛比我，嗰時都無為意張飛個名，之後入咗去睇 反轉腦奇兵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咋咋臨出番去，好柒"},{"pid":"ce60127e35066dcef122ec8b97a8f509e36b4a24","tid":560930,"uid":39576,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T10:30:03.000Z","msg":"咁多人第一次睇pixar既戲..."},{"pid":"5c0b51a318e7ffe5b29688aabebd40b480e4cbae","tid":560930,"uid":59639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T11:02:19.000Z","msg":"睇西片 <br />\n<br />\n播咩火鍋英雄預告片 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n睇睇下個預告咁長嘅 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  走返出去 check <br />\n<br />\n我買嗰套係聽日上 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  收飛嗰個又冇留意"},{"pid":"f8884bccb3a2310a50050619e19b4a2059